<h1 class="article-title">深度丨中国“三航母时代”渐入佳境，硬核实力震慑“台独”分裂势力</h1>
<div class="info">
                            <img src="https://www.sztv.com.cn/ysz/detail_2023/img/line.png">
                            <span class="author">直新闻</span>
                            <span class="time">2025-12-17 23:56:37</span>
                        </div>
<div class="article-content">
<div class="article-body ysz_read_content" id="content"><div id="editWrap" style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: #333333;text-align: justify;text-indent:0 ">
<div class="splat-container" data-ply="aaf619b3745a" style="position:relative;width:100%;min-height:300px;height:56.25vw;max-height:calc(100vw * 9 / 16);background:#0d0d1a;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
