<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; visibility: visible; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; visibility: visible; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;">台防务部门12月17日发布消息称，解放军海军福建舰于16日航经台湾海峡。作为今年11月正式入列的新晋主力，福建舰首次出航即选择穿越台海，其背后的战略深意引发各方揣测。与此同时，“人民海军”官方发布消息确认，山东舰近期圆满完成年度最后一次远海实战化训练，返回三亚某军港。而在不久前，辽宁舰编队在西太平洋抵近日本本土，</span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;">画</span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;">出了一条令世界瞩目的“前所未有”航迹。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; visibility: visible; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; visibility: visible; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;">解放军三艘航母在同一时间段内呈现出高度活跃的态势，这传递出哪些不同寻常的战略信号？深圳卫视直新闻专访特约评论员石宏，为您带来第一手深度解读。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; visibility: visible; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; visibility: visible;"/></span></p>
<section data-tools="" nodeleaf="" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center; visibility: visible; width: 100%;'>
