<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">据台防务部门发布的动态图，福建舰16日自西南向东北穿过台湾海峡。发布中特别强调，这是福建舰今年11月正式入列后的首次出航。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">实际上，这并非福建舰首次过航台海。今年9月上旬，还在海试阶段的中国海军第三艘航母福建舰，就曾通过台湾海峡赴南海海域开展科研试验和训练任务。当时，中国外交部、国防部等都曾就此强调，那次跨区试验训练是航母建造过程中的正常安排，不针对任何特定目标，且完全符合中国国内法和国际法。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">特约评论员石宏认为，福建舰从今年9月10日离开其生产地上海江南造船厂、南下海训，直到入列至今已时间不短。最近这次通过台湾海峡北上，应该是回到船厂进行正常维护，这都属于计划内安排。而从海南三亚到上海，穿过台湾海峡则是必经的最近路线。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">“想想看，从9月10日到现在已经过去3个多月了，毕竟福建舰是一艘刚服役的航母，它回厂进行维护的频率相对来说会比较高。而通过台湾海峡是路程最近的路线，所以也是正常的安排。这么大的一艘全新的航母，技术性能又非常先进，它通过台湾海峡自然对台当局形成了很大的威慑。所以台当局就感到了紧张，其实这就是做贼心虚，因为台当局心里边有鬼，所以它看到福建舰通过台湾海峡才会害怕，”石宏说。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<section data-id="165620" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" data-role="title" data-tools="" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; width: 100%;'>
