<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">据“人民海军”微信公众号17日发布的最新画面显示，海军航母山东舰日前刚刚完成年度最后一次海上训练任务，顺利返回海南三亚某军港。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><img _width="100%" alt="" class="rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif" data-1src1="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/LeO9fTSdguXesmT6eicyclpEVniceSmTSMgn9zNqibuicjibE7UCjNp4nUY5kvp7V2f1Oiax9ZZe0zlIuibhN78FgkXvQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp#imgIndex=1" data-backh="226" data-backw="400" data-fail="0" data-index="4" data-mid="de885f5696ad43978e06651310ebecc7" data-order="0" data-original-style="width:100%;" data-ratio="0.565" data-report-img-idx="2" data-type="image" data-w="400" height="" src="images/7e6dfccd754e.gif" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom; visibility: visible !important;" title="" width=""/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">消息稿中还同步配发了此次海训的最新视频画面。该视频中出现的第一个场景就是山东舰在海面上缓缓行驶，稍远处可隐约看到海岛的轮廓。画面显示，航母尾后还有拖船，可见是航母返航过程中船速下降时借助拖船的帮助前行。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><img _width="100%" alt="" class="rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif" data-1src1="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/LeO9fTSdguXesmT6eicyclpEVniceSmTSMtdkW5wgh8eIZtkX0aKXjDaRICATCb2ic2ZXdwnDcJ1HgmfJwI5k1EPA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp#imgIndex=2" data-backh="226" data-backw="400" data-fail="0" data-index="5" data-mid="eb8ed938874645658a4d73e6ca85a22f" data-order="1" data-original-style="width:100%;" data-ratio="0.565" data-report-img-idx="3" data-type="image" data-w="400" height="" src="images/4065f3f1910f.gif" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom; visibility: visible !important;" title="" width=""/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">深圳卫视直新闻注意到，视频中还披露了山东舰所装备的1130型近防速射炮进行实弹射击的画面。据此前公开披露的信息，该速射炮装有11根炮管、2个弹舱，最大射速能够达到每分钟上万发，即每秒166发，一次能锁定40多个目标，从而对来袭的空中武器进行有效拦截，因此也被视为山东舰最有力的自卫武器之一。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">此外，山东舰舰岛顶部所装“背靠背”382型三坐标对空警戒雷达的工作状态特写，也出现在这次公布的视频当中。画面显示，雷达正在高速旋转，石宏向直新闻分析称，该雷达探测距离很远，而且能够同时探测数百个空中和海面的目标，远程海空警戒能力相当强，再加上它被装在舰岛主桅的顶部，“站得高看得远”，这也表明山东舰在海训时，一直能够对远处的空情海情进行实时掌握。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><img _width="100%" alt="" class="rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif" data-1src1="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/LeO9fTSdguXesmT6eicyclpEVniceSmTSMQ7UribfiapCI8H5rY6NGCCFqtTGhvibgTnjOMKlfrx1GC8sTnnbZUtu0Q/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp#imgIndex=3" data-backh="226" data-backw="400" data-fail="0" data-index="6" data-mid="049520f4d6794e34bbc3cd4642668de9" data-order="2" data-original-style="width:100%;" data-ratio="0.565" data-report-img-idx="4" data-type="image" data-w="400" height="" src="images/eb7073718061.gif" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom; visibility: visible !important;" title="" width=""/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">石宏认为，此次山东舰最新训练画面的一大重头戏，则是同时出现了歼-15T舰载机昼夜起降的场景。这表明，山东舰已经具备全天候起降舰载机的能力，再加上歼-15T舰载机本身出色的技术性能，意味着山东舰所形成的航空作战能力也足够强大。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">“航母在实战的时候，必然是昼夜放飞和回收舰载机的，所以歼-15舰载战斗机在山东舰上进行昼夜起降，就表明山东舰全体系战斗力不光形成了，而且还很强。因为甲板上进行调度也是很关键的，也就是说能够在最短时间内放飞出去，并且能够在最短时间内进行回收。这样一来的话，整个山东舰的飞行甲板运转效率就很高。所以这也可以看出，这次山东舰在海上训练的时候，主要还是在不断强化提升舰载机的作战能力。”</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<section data-id="165620" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" data-role="title" data-tools="" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; width: 100%;'>
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px auto; outline-style: initial; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; width: 25px; height: 5px; background-color: rgb(127, 219, 245);">
<span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span>
</section>
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; display: flex;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; flex-shrink: 0;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; width: 5px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(127, 219, 245);">
<span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span>
</section>
