<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 5px; outline-style: initial; background-color: rgb(232, 244, 255);">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); padding: 9px 25px; outline-style: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(72, 141, 232);transform: translate(-5px, -5px);-webkit-transform: translate(-5px, -5px);-moz-transform: translate(-5px, -5px);-o-transform: translate(-5px, -5px);">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(30, 72, 150); text-align: center;">
<strong data-brushtype="text" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;">入列六周年 山东舰已成远海战略中坚</strong>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">12月17日恰逢山东舰入列六周年纪念日。作为解放军海军第二艘航母，也是中国独立自主设计建造配套的第一艘国产航母，6万吨级常规动力航母山东舰在参考辽宁舰设计理念和运用模式的基础上进一步优化，可搭载更多舰载机，编队指挥能也更上一层楼，为后续研制福建舰打下了坚实基础。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">2019年12月17日，山东舰在海南三亚某军港交付海军，舷号“17”。入列6年以来，山东舰多次穿越岛链，航迹不断向远海延伸，先后参与执行了“联合利剑”“海峡雷霆-2025A”等重大演习演训任务，在与强敌对手较量中，全面提升体系作战能力。在今年的访问香港任务中，山东舰官兵更是向世界人民展现了人民军队威武之师、文明之师、和平之师的良好形象。有军事专家指出，通过持续实战化远洋训练以及双航母编队协同作战验证等，山东舰已突破多项关键技术瓶颈、形成完整作战能力，成为中国海军装备序列中关键的战略威慑力量。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">石宏认为，对于中国海军来说，这是一艘主力航母，很显然它对中国海军走向远海是很关键的。当然了现在有了福建舰，技术水平更高，但是福建舰目前还没有形成战斗力。因此从中国海军航母作战能力方面来讲，目前还是山东舰最强。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><img _width="100%" alt="" class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-1src1="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/nTXBOtRBxAXFkYsS23ym0RJtWwD5FA4FPgj8PqCxTGvJ8JiaFLY5uBI8wdgxqxfyia1ibJTegJuYsmiaic6ho36b82w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp#imgIndex=5" data-backh="771" data-backw="578" data-fail="0" data-index="7" data-mid="8a06f396614d4408b07d33c5fec126f6" data-original-style="width:100%;" data-ratio="1.3333333333333333" data-report-img-idx="7" data-type="image" data-w="1080" height="" src="images/b043ff776aea.jpg" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; vertical-align: bottom; visibility: visible !important;" title="" width=""/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<section data-id="165620" data-pm-slice="0 0 []" data-role="title" data-tools="" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; width: 100%;'>
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px auto; outline-style: initial; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; width: 25px; height: 5px; background-color: rgb(127, 219, 245);">
<span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span>
</section>
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; display: flex;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; flex-shrink: 0;">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; width: 5px; height: 25px; background-color: rgb(127, 219, 245);">
<span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span>
</section>
</section>
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 5px; outline-style: initial; background-color: rgb(232, 244, 255);">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); padding: 9px 25px; outline-style: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(72, 141, 232);transform: translate(-5px, -5px);-webkit-transform: translate(-5px, -5px);-moz-transform: translate(-5px, -5px);-o-transform: translate(-5px, -5px);">
<section data-tools="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(30, 72, 150); text-align: center;">
<strong data-brushtype="text" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;">三舰同辉：中国航母打破“美式部署困境”</strong>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">值得注意的是，解放军航母辽宁舰日前也刚刚结束在西太地区的海训返航东海。此次海训期间，辽宁舰编队选择了</span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">前所未有</span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">的特殊航线，在整个日本南部“划了一个圈”，最近时距离日本本土九州岛仅约400公里。此外还进行了高强度的舰载机起降训练，受到外界高度关注，也给地区挑衅势力予以强烈震慑。结合福建舰与山东舰的最新动向，石宏认为，解放军三艘航母近期都处于活跃状态，这传递出不同寻常的信号，表明中国海军的航母状态非常好、随时可用。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">“这不仅是因为我们的航母都比较年轻，更关键的是有强大的</span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">国力和</span><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">制造业进行支撑，首先设计上非常棒，然后建造质量非常过硬，这才能够保证航母在海试过程中每一次都非常顺利。中国海军在使用过程中也非常注重规范性和科学性，这样一来就使得中国航母始终保持在良好的状态，随时能够拉出来（用）。这一点对于保证中国海军航母战斗力非常关键，”石宏说。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">石宏还以美国海军航母为例进行对比：尽管账面上美国海军有11艘航母，还都是10万吨级的超级航母，但是大部分要么是在维修，要么是等着维修，真正能用的少之又少，现在想凑出3艘以上能用的航母都非常困难，“这就表明美军航母目前状态都很差。”</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;">“总而言之对海军来说，不光是要看航母的数量有多少，还要看能用的航母是什么样子。很显然中国海军现在的这3艘航母都是非常强的，使中国海军能够在航母战斗力上形成良性循环，也就是航母数量在不断增加，航母的战斗力也越来越强。这样一来，很显然海军越来越走向蓝海，我们的整体战斗力是在节节增高的，”石宏说。</span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline-style: initial; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 100%;'><span leaf="" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: ; outline-style: initial;"><br style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); outline-style: initial;"/></span></p>
<section data-pm-slice="0 0 []" data-tools="" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline-style: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; clear: both; min-height: 1em; cursor: text; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; max-inline-size: 100%; width: 100%;'>
